text: Sinusitis means infection or inflammation of the sinuses, which are air-filled spaces inside the bones of the face. There are many symptoms, including thick nasal mucus, a plugged nose, and pain in the face.Rosenfeld R.M. et al 2015. Clinical practice guideline (update): adult sinusitis executive summary".
